      "description": "This vehicle is in good overall condition and has been consistently well-maintained. The engine starts reliably and runs smoothly, and the transmission shifts through all gears without issue, ensuring a dependable driving experience. While the interior is clean and the exterior looks great from a distance, buyers should expect some minor cosmetic wear typical of a used car, such as small paint chips and light interior scuffing. It is a solid, road-ready vehicle that requires no immediate mechanical attention.",
